data.text: “Do you allow exchanges?”  “Can I exchange this item?”  “Exchange policy” "Can I exchange a product?" "What is your exchange policy? " "Do you allow product exchanges?" "I want to exchange my order Can I exchange this item?" "How do I exchange something I bought?" "Is exchange possible?"  "Can I exchange if the size doesn't fit?" "What if I got the wrong item?" "How long is the exchange period?"
